NAME
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::OSPrereqs::Unix - List prereqs for Unix OSes

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.01 of
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::OSPrereqs::Unix (from Perl distribution
    Dist-Zilla-Plugin-OSPrereqs-Unix), released on 2014-12-18.

SYNOPSIS
    In dist.ini:

     [OSPrereqs::Unix]
     Some::Module::That::Runs::On::Unix=0
     Another::Module=1.23

DESCRIPTION
    This module is a subclass of Dist::Zilla::Plugin::OSPrereqs. It is a
    shortcut for doing:

     [OSPrereqs / ~^(linux|freebsd|darwin|...)$]
     ...

    The list of Unix operating systems is retrieved from Perl::osnames.

SEE ALSO
    Dist::Zilla::Plugin::OSPrereqs

    Perl::osnames

